---
---

<section class="bg-white dotted-bg py-20">
  <div class="site-container">

    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center bg-yellow text-ink text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.15em] px-5 py-2 rounded-full mb-6">
        The Real Problem
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight leading-tight text-ink max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        You're losing leads —<br />
        and you don't even <span class="text-red">know it.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-base font-normal leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-6" style="font-weight:400;">
        Every day, leads come in while you're busy. They don't get a reply fast enough. They move on.
        That's not a leads problem — that's a <span class="font-semibold underline">systems</span> problem.
        And most "AI tools" don't fix it. They send the same robotic messages to everyone and make it worse.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stat cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Stat 01 -->
      <div class="relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 pt-10 shadow-sm">
        <span class="absolute -top-3.5 left-5 bg-yellow text-ink text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.15em] px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">
          Stat 01
        </span>
        <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-red/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E63946" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="23 18 13.5 8.5 8.5 13.5 1 6"/>
            <polyline points="17 18 23 18 23 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-5xl font-black text-ink mb-2">40–60%</div>
        <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed" style="font-weight:400;">
          of leads lost — just from slow follow-up. Not because they weren't interested.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stat 02 -->
      <div class="relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 pt-10 shadow-sm">
        <span class="absolute -top-3.5 left-5 bg-yellow text-ink text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.15em] px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">
          Stat 02
        </span>
        <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-red/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E63946" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-5xl font-black text-ink mb-2">2–4 hrs</div>
        <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed" style="font-weight:400;">
          average response time. By then, your competitor already booked them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stat 03 -->
      <div class="relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 pt-10 shadow-sm">
        <span class="absolute -top-3.5 left-5 bg-yellow text-ink text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.15em] px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">
          Stat 03
        </span>
        <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-red/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E63946" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <path d="M16 16s-1.5-2-4-2-4 2-4 2"/>
            <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/>
            <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-5xl font-black text-ink mb-2">$0</div>
        <p class="text-muted text-base leading-relaxed" style="font-weight:400;">
          is what most templated 'AI tools' actually produce after week 2.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
